{
  "stem": "13981.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 22.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was so much paper, there was no other way to carry it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I don't recall that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I have been told this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not really.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We-- you know, we had grown up together and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] had been playing together.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not very much, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not thrown out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I couldn't continue.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Let's put-- after a certain year, after what we would call 10th grade here, which is a certain cut-off point in Germany, was a certain kind of cut-off point in Germany then.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I could go no longer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It wouldn't have been feasible anyhow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We just didn't--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Re-enroll.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My parents were informed that was it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went to work on a farm.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a setup where you were, like, going to school, a farm school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But these were Jewish owners.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not in Recklinghausen.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I worked in two places.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "One was in Silesia, and the other one near Berlin.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we were taught a little theory in farming and also had to do the hard practical work that goes with it, like plowing, hoeing weeds.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you mention it, and we had to do it-- threshing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Milking cows.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, when I was a kid, I had a little vacation job here, there, trying to earn a little pocket money, but no job, as such, to live on.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were very fortunate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother had three brothers who had left Germany before the turn of the century.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In fact, the first one came over in 1890 or so.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Bernalillo, New Mexico.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Bernalillo's about 20 miles north from-- of Albuquerque.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they, of course, knew much more what was going on in Germany, due to the news media than we in Germany knew.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
